## Test Checklist

- [ ] Register a new user -> 200 with success
- [ ] Register with duplicate email -> 409
- [ ] Register with short password (< 6 chars) -> 400
- [ ] Login with valid credentials -> JWT token returned
- [ ] Login with wrong password -> 401
- [ ] Login with unknown email -> 401
- [ ] Login with email having whitespace -> still works (trimmed)
- [ ] Login with uppercase email -> still works (lowered)
- [ ] GET /api/auth/me with valid token -> user data
- [ ] GET /api/auth/me without token -> 401
- [ ] GET /api/auth/me with invalid token -> 401
- [ ] SQL injection attempt in email -> 401 (not auth)
- [ ] Token survives page reload (localStorage)
